{"tid":2376712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府正研究為接種新冠疫苗人士購買保險","createTime":"2021-01-23T04:20:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T04:57:33.000Z","uid":90497,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b666fb2f98a656d0bed40d32c9bf70a08bc11c47","tid":2376712,"uid":90497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T04:20:37.000Z","msg":"對於新冠病毒疫苗接種工作，歐陽瑜表示，特區政府正研究為接種新冠病毒疫苗人士購買保險，費用由政府支付，並已經與保險業界商討，當有合適的方案會向社會公佈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.mo/zh-hant/news/361790/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.mo%2Fzh-hant%2Fnews%2F361790%2F&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5C3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=afde5da8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.mo/zh-hant/news/361790/</a><br />\n<br />\n政府洗錢日日 用TVB 宣傳疫苗，叫人打大陸疫苗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澳門政府就直接洗錢幫市民買保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e3cf3984643b3ec4a674426deccdb032435ffa","tid":2376712,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T04:26:44.000Z","msg":"出事就話證明唔到有關"},{"pid":"c5699d48cf978aac2fc275dc1eb178ca440eb32d","tid":2376712,"uid":268516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T04:57:33.000Z","msg":"中人壽海外？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買完然後樣樣話唔保 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}